    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/63c159cca4e9e5b7ed0c03c9973d3a89.avif?t=1765277844\" width=600 height=108 /></span><br>全体怪奇萌版叙事游戏粉丝火速集结！<br>这段惊悚冒险故事的主人公是捣蛋鬼快递员汤姆，她在送快递的过程中总是怪事频出。说来也难怪，她是名副其实的跟踪狂，一有机会就爱窥探别人隐私。与她同行，发现当地居民不可告人的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/8cd8f83d936fa941f9bc737cf7f20918.avif?t=1765277844\" width=600 height=108 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/5ac0fac80d83d5b577da6d1c3842b34b.avif?t=1765277844\" width=600 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/2afb8db6f0e440ceeafdea8855705371.poster.avif?t=1765277844\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/2afb8db6f0e440ceeafdea8855705371.webm?t=1765277844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>探索</strong><br>沉浸在独具特色的手绘世界当中。探索众多充满神秘色彩的地方和秘境。逐帧动画为这个世界烘托出复古气氛，让你置身于怪事连连的诡异村庄之中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/15e5068029b41b01da672025b7e08c85.poster.avif?t=1765277844\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/15e5068029b41b01da672025b7e08c85.webm?t=1765277844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>窥探</strong><br>俗话说好奇心害死猫，可汤姆就是这样一个吃瓜群众。跟随她的脚步，你将目睹千奇百怪的场景，而且一个比一个匪夷所思。一桩桩奇闻会令你望而却步吗？事实恰恰相反。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/f5c0fcdc291d191bcb0d32c9f1da09e7.poster.avif?t=1765277844\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/f5c0fcdc291d191bcb0d32c9f1da09e7.webm?t=1765277844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>送货</strong><br>陪同汤姆出勤工作，为疯狂村民派送包裹。这份工作给了你近距离窥探他人私密生活的完美借口。但你能抵挡住拆包裹的诱惑吗？ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257440/extras/eedc990eea5f97cac38ec8a7793dfcee.avif?t=1765277844\" width=617 height=104 /></span>",
